HEADWORD: Emplacement
<hw>Em*place"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>emplacement</ets>.]</ety> <def>A putting in, or assigning to, a
definite place; localization; <as>as, the <ex>emplacement</ex> of a
structure</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
